# outputs

**Instance Property**

The outputs from which you read media data.

## Declaration

```swift
var outputs: [AVAssetReaderOutput] { get }
```

## Discussion

The array contains the concrete instances of [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVAssetReaderOutput] that you associate with the reader.

## Managing outputs

- **canAdd(_:)**: Determines whether you can add the output to the asset reader.
- **add(_:)**: Adds an output to the reader.
